Class ComparisonService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.scheid.jsondiff.service.ComparisonService

  • @Service
public class ComparisonService
extends java.lang.Object
    Service to interface components that execute the comparison. Persists the Comparison and its Elements.

      • compare

        public ComparisonResult compare(java.lang.String comparisonIdentifier)
        Compares all Elements found on the Comparison with the provided identifier. At least two valid Elements are required for a comparison. A comparison error, if present, will be returned.
        Parameters:
        comparisonIdentifier - Identifier for the Comparison to be processed.
        Returns:
        ComparisonResult The comparison result for each Element found.

        Parameters:

        Returns:
        Comparison The complete comparison, with its Elements

      • addElement

        public Comparison addElement(java.lang.String base64String,
                             java.lang.String comparisonIdentifier,
                             Position position)
        Add a new Element to a Comparison. The provided value will replace a previous element if the provided position was already occupied on the comparison.
        Parameters:
        base64String - Element value assumed to be a JSON base64 encoded binary data.
        comparisonIdentifier - Unique identifier for the Comparison.
        position - Element's Position in the Comparison.
        Returns:
        Comparison The updated or created comparison, with its Elements

      • addElement

        public Comparison addElement(java.lang.String base64String,
                             java.lang.String comparisonIdentifier)
        Add a new Element to a Comparison with the provided element's value and comparison's identifier. The provided value will not assume a fixed Position and will not replace any previous elements in the comparison.
        Parameters:
        base64String - Element value assumed to be a JSON base64 encoded binary data.
        comparisonIdentifier - Unique identifier for the Comparison.
        Returns:
        Comparison The updated or created comparison, with its Elements

        true if the Comparison was successfully deleted.
